[node name="SmartLabel" parent="4" index="1" instance=ExtResource("7_67axm")]
offset_top = 243.0
offset_bottom = 977.0
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "Taylor's a medic. The [i]herbs[/i] that grow on Leylines are potent, and sought out by those of her profession.

[i]Nate[/i] nearly got himself [i]electrocuted[/i] not an hour ago trying to pull up an old LCD with a touch of Leyline
in it. Leylines and electronics do [i]not[/i] mix well.

Well. That's not quite true, is it? There is the matter of your [i]knack[/i]. None of the human engineers have found
the trick of it, but as long as you can remember, [i]you've[/i] been able to coax the Leyline into recharging
electronics.

Electronics [i]it[/i] isn't currently possessing, that is. Grabbing electronics [i]from[/i] a Leyline will electrocute
you as surely as it would Nate.

People die that way. It's not something to mess with."

