[node name="SmartLabel" parent="5" index="3" instance=ExtResource("7_67axm")]
offset_top = 211.0
offset_right = 950.0
offset_bottom = 587.0
bbcode_enabled = true
text = "But then, you can [i]see[/i] the Leylines, and Nate can't. He has to carefully check with a multimeter--[i]estimate[/i] how much residual flicker is safe.

[i]Elves[/i] can see the Leyline. [i]Elves[/i] can interface with magic.

It's been alienating you from the others ever since you came to the humans."

[node name="SmartLabel2" parent="5" index="4" instance=ExtResource("7_67axm")]
